data.title: Photo taken at Caminho da Trincheira 1, 9300 Câmara de Lobos, Portugal with Panasonic DMC
data.meta_description: The photo was taken using a Panasonic DMC-TZ10 camera at Caminho da Trincheira 1, 9300 Câmara de Lobos, Portugal.
data.text:
The photo was shot using a Panasonic DMC-TZ10 camera at an aperture of f/6.3, 1/400 sec. shutter speed and ISO 125. Flash did not fire, auto mode. The original image file has a resolution of 3392 x 2264 pixels, or in other words 7.7 megapixels.The photo has a resolution of 180 DPI.

According to the image metadata, the photo was shot on Wednesday 13th of July 2011. The local time was 16:53:14. The timezone was Atlantic / Madeira, which is GMT +01:00. Please note that timezone was guessed using the GPS coordinates and may not be accurate. The EXIF timestamp may also be wrong if the date and time weren't set correctly in the digital camera.

Panasonic DMC-TZ10 camera has a built-in GPS receiver and allows geotagging on image files. The coordinates and location where the photo was taken is stored in the EXIF. According to GPS data analysis, the photo was taken at coordinates 32° 38' 49.82" N , 16° 58' 27.63" W. The elevation was 0 meters. Using reverse geocoding, the address associated with the coordinates is guessed as Caminho da Trincheira 1, 9300 Câmara de Lobos, Portugal. Depending on the GPS receiver and the reception conditions the accuracy may vary and the address should not be regarded as exact location.
